          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Relative population  of  states  in 11B following the",
                " 12C(gamma,p) reaction has  ben  measured  with  high",
                " resolution    using   the   deexcitation   gamma-ray",
                " technique.  The states near 7  MeV  in  11B  clearly",
                " resolved   and  the  measured  population  clarifies",
                " earlier conflicting data.  Comparison of the results",
                " with  new  calculations  indicates the importance of",
                " both one-nucleon and multinucleon processes."
              ]
            }
          ],
